@node "Intro" "Description"
   This multimedia player is programmed with Hollywood and it is  with part of source code
 from Andreas Falkenhahn examples  to VideoPlayer and AnimPlayer,  I make this little tool
 to demostrates the multimedia optios of this programming language it isn't a sustitute of
 other best videoplayers but altmost.

  V.A.M.P. display the next multimedia formats currently:

    * Amiga Anim formats: anim-anim5-ham6-ham8

    * MovieSetter movies format.

    * Gif anims.

    * Show pictures: jpg, png, gif, lbm, bmp, svg.

    * Video formats: avi-mov-mpeg-mpg-wmv-flv-mp4-DivX.
@endnode


